  <!-- ============ Information: Contacts ======== -->
  <sect1 id="anjuta-contacts">
   <title>Contacts</title>
   <para>
    For the time being you can contact me for anything at my personal
    email <email>kh_naba@123india.com</email>. Just make sure your mail
    has a very brief and descriptive subject line. Please do mail me
    and tell how do you like Anjuta. 
   </para>
   <para>
    You can also visit Anjuta home website at:
    <ulink type="http" url="http://anjuta.sourceforge.net">http://anjuta.sourceforge.net</ulink>
    You will also find the details of Anjuta at Project site:
    <ulink type="http" url="http://www.sourceforge.net/projects/anjuta">
    http://www.sourceforge.net/projects/anjuta</ulink>
   </para>
